[{"Code":"en","Title":"Payment sessions lifecycle","Slug":"payment-sessions-lifecycle","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"0fc6f4b6-a832-4565-bcb7-6a7da305fc8f\">A payment session's status changes throughout its lifecycle, marking different stages of the payment or linking process.</p><p data-block-id=\"a7865ec4-64cc-470e-9394-ed4ee4d323d6\"><img data-block-id=\"4c0c090e-3038-4507-9024-6a979ae5ee2f\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-11-28-090900.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:527px;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"e671938d-413d-462f-9787-797db4e45b08\"></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"922\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:922px;width:922px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:137px;\"><col style=\"width:482px;\"><col style=\"width:303px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"a1062efd-1254-4d30-bf01-a6b8c0c8bc95\"><strong>Status</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"14d68e57-b849-483b-9aab-7ec3f21d89c0\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"d68d0874-ce68-4a73-8efc-ca27249425d5\">Webhook event</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"49ebab0d-bda6-4669-9c0c-5a4fb473e340\"><strong>Active</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"2485b4f2-e0a8-4b45-ac2f-5b57dca766bc\">The Payment Session status will be <strong>ACTIVE</strong> immediately after creation. It remains active until it is successfully completed, expires (based on the <code>expiry_date</code>), or is manually canceled.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"ad854611-7c2d-417a-8028-b00b8d55a9f7\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"aad4dc57-e811-4663-a2a1-33d92796aa89\"><strong>Completed</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"5665261d-ae69-43fc-b0de-c3763976c13c\">The status changes to <strong>COMPLETED</strong> when the payment or linking process (depending on the chosen flow) is successfully finished. If the user fails during the process, they can retry within the same session. During this state you will receive <code>payment_session.completed</code> webhook to identify you the state transition.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"271c7787-d9f0-4b7d-b5cf-06eab97c9412\"><code>payment_session.completed</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"276b9efe-b487-405f-baa8-5a25ea7b450a\"><strong>Expired</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"57da9bf2-6d70-4e6f-8e6d-5a24a5c82170\">The status changes to <strong>EXPIRED</strong> when the <code>expiry_date</code> set during Payment Session creation is reached, and an expired Payment Session cannot be reactivated. During this state you will receive <code>payment_session.expired</code> webhook to identify you the state transition.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"bb4dd8e5-91cf-4d25-9722-82ecf2e80e44\"><code>payment_session.expired</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"cf0c9862-4166-4f51-ac92-9f5fec0c31b5\"><strong>Canceled</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"a1aaa6ec-caff-4a7d-afc3-5f7e8bc9046b\">If the Payment Session is manually canceled, the status changes to <strong>CANCELED </strong>immediately. The end user will no longer have access to the <code>payment_link_url</code>, and a canceled Payment Session cannot be reactivated.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"4be5e4b9-8845-4939-bb5a-08e247a9179a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"79c6adbf-c406-46c1-8f66-edce74224fee\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Payment sessions lifecycle","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Lifecycle payment sessions","Slug":"payment-sessions-lifecycle","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcbgsf35-1tife5-022\">Pada lifecycle Payment Session, status dapat berubah berdasarkan setiap tahap proses pembayaran.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazuz-y9gqap-003\"><img data-block-id=\"mcbfazv0-yhylmy-004\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-11-28-090900.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:527px;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mcbfazv1-tqzwvh-005\"></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"922\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:922px;width:922px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:137px;\"><col style=\"width:482px;\"><col style=\"width:303px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv1-ply2cj-006\"><strong>Status</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv2-sk0p3u-007\"><strong>Deskripsi</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv2-cdffg7-008\">Event webhook</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbgu97q-78isfs-023\"><strong>Active</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv2-1lnkho-010\">Status payment session akan menjadi <strong>ACTIVE</strong> segera setelah pembuatan. Itu tetap aktif hingga berhasil diselesaikan, kedaluwarsa (berdasarkan <code>expiry_date</code>), atau dibatalkan secara manual.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv2-ks5n64-011\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbgu97q-cv6e6v-024\"><strong>Completed</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv3-yftzsb-013\">Status berubah menjadi <strong>COMPLETED</strong> ketika proses pembayaran atau penautan (tergantung pada alur yang dipilih) berhasil diselesaikan. Jika pengguna gagal selama proses, mereka dapat mencoba lagi dalam sesi yang sama. Selama keadaan ini Anda akan menerima <code>payment_session.completed</code> webhook untuk mengidentifikasi transisi status Anda.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv3-0b3zft-014\"><code>payment_session.completed</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbgu97q-xtdvel-025\"><strong>Expired</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv4-km617d-016\">Status berubah menjadi <strong>EXPIRED</strong> ketika <code>expiry_date</code> tercapai, dan payment session yang kedaluwarsa tidak dapat diaktifkan kembali. Selama keadaan ini Anda akan menerima webhook <code>payment_session.expired</code> untuk mengidentifikasi transisi status Anda.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv4-khe7jh-017\"><code>payment_session.expired</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbgu97q-491187-026\"><strong>Canceled</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv4-mhjh98-019\">Jika payment session dibatalkan secara manual, status akan segera berubah menjadi <strong>CANCELED</strong>. Pengguna akhir tidak akan lagi memiliki akses ke <code>payment_link_url</code>, dan payment session yang dibatalkan tidak dapat diaktifkan kembali.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv5-40tr4u-020\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mcbfazv5-k0f39m-021\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Lifecycle payment sessions","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"วงจรชีวิตของเซสชันการชำระเงิน","Slug":"payment-sessions-lifecycle","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0fc6f4b6-a832-4565-bcb7-6a7da305fc8f\">สถานะของ Payment Session จะเปลี่ยนแปลงตลอดวงจรชีวิต (lifecycle) โดยระบุขั้นตอนต่างๆ ของกระบวนการชำระเงินหรือการเชื่อมโยง (linking process)</p><p data-block-id=\"a7865ec4-64cc-470e-9394-ed4ee4d323d6\"><img data-block-id=\"4c0c090e-3038-4507-9024-6a979ae5ee2f\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-11-28-090900.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:527px;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"e671938d-413d-462f-9787-797db4e45b08\"></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"922\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:922px;width:922px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:137px;\"><col style=\"width:482px;\"><col style=\"width:303px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"a1062efd-1254-4d30-bf01-a6b8c0c8bc95\"><strong>Status (สถานะ)</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"14d68e57-b849-483b-9aab-7ec3f21d89c0\"><strong>Description (คำอธิบาย)</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"d68d0874-ce68-4a73-8efc-ca27249425d5\">Webhook event</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"49ebab0d-bda6-4669-9c0c-5a4fb473e340\"><strong>Active</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"2485b4f2-e0a8-4b45-ac2f-5b57dca766bc\">สถานะ Payment Session จะเป็น **ACTIVE** ทันทีหลังจากสร้างขึ้น สถานะจะยังคงเป็น Active จนกว่าจะเสร็จสมบูรณ์ (successfully completed) หมดอายุ (expires) (ตาม <code>expiry_date</code>) หรือถูกยกเลิกด้วยตนเอง (manually canceled)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"ad854611-7c2d-417a-8028-b00b8d55a9f7\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"aad4dc57-e811-4663-a2a1-33d92796aa89\"><strong>Completed</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"5665261d-ae69-43fc-b0de-c3763976c13c\">สถานะจะเปลี่ยนเป็น **COMPLETED** เมื่อกระบวนการชำระเงินหรือการเชื่อมโยง (ขึ้นอยู่กับ flow ที่เลือก) เสร็จสมบูรณ์ หากผู้ใช้ล้มเหลวในระหว่างกระบวนการ พวกเขาสามารถลองใหม่ได้ภายในเซสชันเดียวกัน ในสถานะนี้ คุณจะได้รับ webhook <code>payment_session.completed</code> เพื่อระบุการเปลี่ยนสถานะ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"271c7787-d9f0-4b7d-b5cf-06eab97c9412\"><code>payment_session.completed</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"276b9efe-b487-405f-baa8-5a25ea7b450a\"><strong>Expired</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"57da9bf2-6d70-4e6f-8e6d-5a24a5c82170\">สถานะจะเปลี่ยนเป็น **EXPIRED** เมื่อถึง <code>expiry_date</code> ที่กำหนดไว้ระหว่างการสร้าง Payment Session และ Payment Session ที่หมดอายุแล้วจะไม่สามารถเปิดใช้งานใหม่ได้ ในสถานะนี้ คุณจะได้รับ webhook <code>payment_session.expired</code> เพื่อระบุการเปลี่ยนสถานะ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"bb4dd8e5-91cf-4d25-9722-82ecf2e80e44\"><code>payment_session.expired</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"cf0c9862-4166-4f51-ac92-9f5fec0c31b5\"><strong>Canceled</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"a1aaa6ec-caff-4a7d-afc3-5f7e8bc9046b\">หาก Payment Session ถูกยกเลิกด้วยตนเอง สถานะจะเปลี่ยนเป็น **CANCELED** ทันที ผู้ใช้ปลายทางจะไม่สามารถเข้าถึง <code>payment_link_url</code> ได้อีกต่อไป และ Payment Session ที่ถูกยกเลิกแล้วจะไม่สามารถเปิดใช้งานใหม่ได้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"4be5e4b9-8845-4939-bb5a-08e247a9179a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"79c6adbf-c406-46c1-8f66-edce74224fee\"></p>","SeoTitle":"วงจรชีวิตของเซสชันการชำระเงิน","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Ciclo de vida de las Payment Sessions","Slug":"payment-sessions-lifecycle","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0fc6f4b6-a832-4565-bcb7-6a7da305fc8f\">El estado de una Payment Session cambia a lo largo de su ciclo de vida, marcando diferentes etapas del proceso de pago o vinculación.</p><p data-block-id=\"a7865ec4-64cc-470e-9394-ed4ee4d323d6\"><img data-block-id=\"4c0c090e-3038-4507-9024-6a979ae5ee2f\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-11-28-090900.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:527px;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"e671938d-413d-462f-9787-797db4e45b08\"></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"922\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:922px;width:922px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:137px;\"><col style=\"width:482px;\"><col style=\"width:303px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"a1062efd-1254-4d30-bf01-a6b8c0c8bc95\"><strong>Estado</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"14d68e57-b849-483b-9aab-7ec3f21d89c0\"><strong>Descripción</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"d68d0874-ce68-4a73-8efc-ca27249425d5\">Webhook event</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"49ebab0d-bda6-4669-9c0c-5a4fb473e340\"><strong>Active</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"2485b4f2-e0a8-4b45-ac2f-5b57dca766bc\">El estado de la Payment Session será <strong>ACTIVO</strong> inmediatamente después de su creación. Permanece activo hasta que se completa exitosamente, expira (según la <code>expiry_date</code>), o se cancela manualmente.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"ad854611-7c2d-417a-8028-b00b8d55a9f7\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"aad4dc57-e811-4663-a2a1-33d92796aa89\"><strong>Completed</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"5665261d-ae69-43fc-b0de-c3763976c13c\">El estado cambia a <strong>COMPLETADO</strong> cuando el proceso de pago o vinculación (dependiendo del flujo elegido) finaliza exitosamente. Si el usuario falla durante el proceso, puede reintentarlo dentro de la misma sesión. Durante este estado, usted recibirá el webhook <code>payment_session.completed</code> para identificar la transición de estado.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"271c7787-d9f0-4b7d-b5cf-06eab97c9412\"><code>payment_session.completed</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"276b9efe-b487-405f-baa8-5a25ea7b450a\"><strong>Expired</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"57da9bf2-6d70-4e6f-8e6d-5a24a5c82170\">El estado cambia a <strong>EXPIRADO</strong> cuando se alcanza la <code>expiry_date</code> establecida durante la creación de la Payment Session, y una Payment Session expirada no puede reactivarse. Durante este estado, usted recibirá el webhook <code>payment_session.expired</code> para identificar la transición de estado.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"bb4dd8e5-91cf-4d25-9722-82ecf2e80e44\"><code>payment_session.expired</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"137\"><p data-block-id=\"cf0c9862-4166-4f51-ac92-9f5fec0c31b5\"><strong>Canceled</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"482\"><p data-block-id=\"a1aaa6ec-caff-4a7d-afc3-5f7e8bc9046b\">Si la Payment Session se cancela manualmente, el estado cambia a <strong>CANCELADO</strong> inmediatamente. El usuario final ya no tendrá acceso a la <code>payment_link_url</code>, y una Payment Session cancelada no puede reactivarse.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"303\"><p data-block-id=\"4be5e4b9-8845-4939-bb5a-08e247a9179a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"79c6adbf-c406-46c1-8f66-edce74224fee\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Ciclo de vida de las Payment Sessions","Description":null}]